  "description": {
    "short": "MCP HTTP bridge — lets Claude Code drive Fusion 360 via AI",
    "long": "Starts a local HTTP server on port 4176 that exposes Fusion 360 operations (sketch, extrude, revolve, boolean, fillet, export) as a REST API. Pair with the fusion360-mcp TypeScript server to drive Fusion from Claude Code."
